msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-12-quarkus-insights-247-agentic-orchestration.adoc
msgid "**MCP Tools**: Agents have access to https://modelcontextprotocol.io/[Model Context Protocol] tools"
msgstr ""

