#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-05-12-quarkus-insights-247-agentic-orchestration.adoc
msgid "Performance Considerations"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-12-quarkus-insights-247-agentic-orchestration.adoc
msgid ""
"**Challenges with distributed agents:**\n"
"- Initial democratic approach was slow (15+ minutes for simple queries)\n"
"- Each agent loading context independently created overhead\n"
"- Trade-off between flexibility and performance"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-05-12-quarkus-insights-247-agentic-orchestration.adoc
msgid ""
"**Optimizations:**\n"
"- Selective agent participation based on question relevance\n"
"- Agents can \"bow out\" if not relevant to the query\n"
"- Running entirely on local GPUs (no cloud API costs)"
msgstr ""

